<h3>Apa itu konsep layanan kesehatan tradisional?</h3>
<p>Konsep ini menangani penyakit secara holistik, bertujuan untuk meningkatkan kualitas hidup melalui metode alami dan komplementer.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-13T09:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-14T16:05:05Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/traditional-and-modern-medical-approaches-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Pendekatan Kedokteran Tradisional dan Modern di Turki","title":"traditional-and-modern-medical-approaches-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'id' AND "slug" = 'pendekatan-kedokteran-tradisional-dan-modern-di-turki' );
