<p>It&#8217;s necessary to read plenty of books, write a daily journal, memorize vocabulary, and engage in Turkish speaking practice.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-05-30T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:52:43Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'methods-for-thinking-in-the-target-language-while-learning-turkish' );
